    <title>利用Caddy完美实现Trojan与V2ray共存</title>
    <link href="https://siemenstutorials.github.io/posts/47385.html"/>
    <id>https://siemenstutorials.github.io/posts/47385.html</id>
    <published>2020-05-03T21:17:55.000Z</published>
    <updated>2020-05-04T23:38:52.377Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="利用Caddy完美实现Trojan与V2ray共存"><a href="#利用Caddy完美实现Trojan与V2ray共存" class="headerlink" title="利用Caddy完美实现Trojan与V2ray共存"></a><center>利用Caddy完美实现Trojan与V2ray共存</center></h1><h2 id="视频教程"><a href="#视频教程" class="headerlink" title="视频教程"></a><center><a href="https://youtu.be/YuZ4TEayfGw" target="_blank" rel="noopener">视频教程</a></center></h2><p>1：准备工具域名1个；VPS一个（系统镜像ubuntu16.0+）;<br>请先将域名解析至VPS,并确定解析成功后再进行搭建。</p><p>2：安装Docker与Docker Compose；<br>Docker安装脚本：</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">apt-get update</span><br><span class="line">apt-get install docker.io</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>Docker Compose安装脚本：</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">curl -L https://github.com/docker/compose/releases/download/1.21.2/docker-compose-$(uname -s)-$(uname -m) -o /usr/<span class="built_in">local</span>/bin/docker-compose</span><br><span class="line">chmod +x /usr/<span class="built_in">local</span>/bin/docker-compose</span><br><span class="line">docker-compose --version</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>3:Git工具安装以及源码下载：</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">apt-get install git</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>源码下载</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">git <span class="built_in">clone</span> https://github.com/maidoudouo/V2ray_Trojan_Docker</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>4：域名设置<br>进入目录</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="built_in">cd</span> V2ray_Trojan_Docker</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>然后启动设置</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">./OneKeySet.sh</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>5：启动Docker<br>运行脚本</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">docker-compose up -d</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>6：配置信息查看：<br>vi info.txt</p><p>若要修改配置信息请先cd V2ray_Trojan_Docker；<br>1：在caddy/Caddyfile中修改Caddy修改域名；<br>2：在v2ray/config.json中修改V2Ray的UUID；<br>3：在trojan/config/config.json中修改Trojan的密码、证书路径、域名。</p><p>(本文脚本源于<a href="https://github.com/maidoudouo/V2ray_Trojan_Docker" target="_blank" rel="noopener">maidoudouo</a>;在此感谢大神的辛勤付出)</p><h2 id="SiemensTutorials"><a href="#SiemensTutorials" class="headerlink" title="SiemensTutorials"></a><center><a href="https://www.youtube.com/SiemensTutorials" target="_blank" rel="noopener">SiemensTutorials</a></center></h2><h2 id="星际云网络加速"><a href="#星际云网络加速" class="headerlink" title="星际云网络加速"></a><center><a href="https://www.xjycloud.xyz" target="_blank" rel="noopener">星际云网络加速</a></center></h2>]]></content>
    
