  <entry>
    <title>Trojan+v2ray+SSR单VPS共存</title>
    <link href="https://siemenstutorials.github.io/posts/46908.html"/>
    <id>https://siemenstutorials.github.io/posts/46908.html</id>
    <published>2020-05-02T01:08:41.000Z</published>
    <updated>2020-05-04T23:38:28.057Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<iframe width="560" height="315" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/hSqO8ppMYyc" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen></iframe><h1 id="Trojan-v2ray-SSR单VPS共存"><a href="#Trojan-v2ray-SSR单VPS共存" class="headerlink" title="Trojan+v2ray+SSR单VPS共存"></a><center>Trojan+v2ray+SSR单VPS共存</center></h1><p> 准备工具：域名1个/VPS一台(CentOS7)<br>视频教程：<a href="https://youtu.be/hSqO8ppMYyc" target="_blank" rel="noopener">YouTube</a><br>1:域名解析到VPS；解析要充分，以便全球生效！</p><p>2：安装BBR PLUS加速（可选）</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">wget <span class="string">"https://github.com/chiakge/Linux-NetSpeed/raw/master/tcp.sh"</span> &amp;&amp; chmod +x tcp.sh &amp;&amp; ./tcp.sh</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>3:大神atrandys一键安装Trojan脚本：<br>若提示无wget,则运行：</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">yum -y install wget</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>然后再运行下面Docker版Trojan一键安装脚本:</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">curl -O https://raw.githubusercontent.com/atrandys/trojan/master/trojan_install.sh &amp;&amp; chmod +x trojan_install.sh &amp;&amp; ./trojan_install.sh</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>4：运行大神Docker的UI管理Portainer一键脚本：</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">docker run -d -p 9000:9000 -v /var/run/docker.sock:/var/run/docker.sock \</span><br><span class="line">--name ui --restart=always lihaixin/portainer:me</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>5：浏览器运行<a href="https://VPS_IP:9000;设置密码并创建帐户，然后选择local。">https://VPS_IP:9000;设置密码并创建帐户，然后选择local。</a></p><p>6:在容器containers中可以看到安装的Trojan；在App Templates中可以选择V2ray、SSR、Brook等代理程序</p><p>8：客户端下载<br><a href="https://drive.google.com/open?id=1m9b6n9KnWI40octuo6IWAWqWdWxseLLk" target="_blank" rel="noopener">SS客户端</a><br><a href="https://drive.google.com/open?id=15sRZ7Sf9CVO0IdELNEvgD7xLxCxMqUVO" target="_blank" rel="noopener">V2ray客户端下载</a></p><h1 id="星际云网络速"><a href="#星际云网络速" class="headerlink" title="星际云网络速"></a><a href="https://www.xjycloud.xyz" target="_blank" rel="noopener">星际云网络速</a></h1><h2 id="Trojan科学上网节点搭建视频教程"><a href="#Trojan科学上网节点搭建视频教程" class="headerlink" title="Trojan科学上网节点搭建视频教程"></a><a href="https://youtu.be/esr4bDuZj34" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Trojan科学上网节点搭建视频教程</a></h2><h2 id="SiemensTutorials"><a href="#SiemensTutorials" class="headerlink" title="SiemensTutorials"></a><center><a href="https://www.youtube.com/SiemensTutorials" target="_blank" rel="noopener">SiemensTutorials</a></center></h2><h2 id="星际云网络加速"><a href="#星际云网络加速" class="headerlink" title="星际云网络加速"></a><center><a href="https://www.xjycloud.xyz" target="_blank" rel="noopener">星际云网络加速</a></center></h2>]]></content>
    
